div.h3: PCMPESTRI (Packed Compare Explicit Length Strings, Return Index)
div.p: This SIMD instruction performs advanced string processing in hardware.

ol.li: Explicit Length: Lengths of both operands are provided in EAX and EDX, allowing for strings with null bytes.

Aggregation Units:
Equal Any: Character set search (find any char from XMM0 in XMM1).
Equal Ordered: Substring search (find XMM0 in XMM1).

Result Propagation:
The first matching index is loaded into ECX.
CF flag is set if a match is found.
ZF flag is set if a null character is found in XMM1.
